  "title": "DevOps Engineer (GitHub / Azure DevOps)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We are looking for a DevOps Engineer todesign, build, and maintain CI/CD pipelines using GitHub Actions or AzureDevOps. You will enable fast, reliable, and automated software delivery acrossmultiple environments.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>·       Build and manage CI/CDpipelines for application and infrastructure deployments</p><p>·       Automate testing, packaging,and release workflows</p><p>·       Implement DevSecOps practicesincluding vulnerability, dependency, and code-quality scanning</p><p>·       Manage GitHub/Azure DevOpsenvironments, runners, and artifacts</p><p>·       Support containerization usingDocker and Kubernetes</p><p>·       Collaborate with developmentteams to streamline build and deployment processes</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>·       Min 5 years of DevOps orbuild/release engineering experience</p><p>·       Strong hands-on GitHub Actionsand/or Azure DevOps pipeline expertise</p><p>·       Knowledge of YAML, Docker,Kubernetes, Terraform</p><p>·       Understanding of cloudfundamentals (Azure/AWS)</p><p>·       Familiarity with securityscanning tools and DevSecOps principle</p>",
